-11T05:04:37.950Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/1043","id":1001,"attachmentType":"image/jpeg","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/宋國鼎3_工作區域 1.jpg","attachmentName":"87e95e15-d19b-42e0-9bba-55247bedc6dd_.jpg","title":" ","content":null,"weight":3,"createdAt":"2022-08-11T03:44:42.785Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/1042","id":1000,"attachmentType":"image/jpeg","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/宋國鼎2_工作區域 1.jpg","attachmentName":"1b015411-a6f4-499a-b918-54a383b82a0b_.jpg","title":" ","content":null,"weight":2,"createdAt":"2022-08-11T03:44:41.200Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/1041","id":999,"attachmentType":"image/jpeg","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/宋國鼎1_工作區域 1.jpg","attachmentName":"a69416ac-334b-484a-a212-153464c77060_.jpg","title":" ","content":null,"weight":1,"createdAt":"2022-08-11T03:43:56.959Z"}],"candidateContacts":[{"id":1005,"title":"電話","content":"037-465-009 <br> 037-370-147","createdAt":"2022-08-09T05:47:42.732Z"},{"id":1006,"title":"地址","content":"苗栗縣竹南鎮立達街186號 <br> 苗栗縣苗栗市中正路474號","createdAt":"2022-08-09T05:47:42.790Z"}],"candidateDeclaration":{"id":998,"title":"一起贏得苗栗的驕傲！","content":"<p>我在苗栗出生長大，在外地求學後，又回到家鄉執業律師，</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>執業第一年就碰上關廠工人案。當時勞委會出動80多名律師，提告將近630件案件，苗栗也是其中的主戰場之一。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>我沒有考慮太多就辭去受雇律師工作，全力替伯伯、阿姨辯護，爭取應有的權益。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>接著我陸續參與苗栗許多社運案件的義務辯護，包含苑裡反風車、大埔案等等。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>2018年，我代表時代力量參選苗栗縣議員，順利進入議會。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>四年的議員任期，我在議會監督縣府，在地方服務選民、爭取建設，也協助造橋反坤輿掩埋場自救會的抗爭。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>三年多來，我陪著自救會南征北討、四處陳情，歷經多次暴力衝突，隨著高等行政法院判決自救會勝訴，這場惡夢才劃下句點。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>四年下來我很清楚，苗栗有非常好的自然環境，有篤實勇敢的人民，問題就出在政治。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>是派系世襲、黑金勾結的政治環境，扼殺了苗栗的發展，殘害善良的苗栗人民。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>繼續連任議員並不難，但我想要為自己的家鄉拼一次。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>我要競逐苗栗縣長，透過這場選戰，改變苗栗的選舉文化，改變苗栗的政治文化，喚醒被派系政治麻痺數十年的苗栗。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>只有乾淨的政治才能帶來乾淨的環境，只有不講空話、誠信正直的領導者，才能帶領苗栗面對數十年的沈屙，帶來全新的未來。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>請所有的苗栗朋友相信自己，相信自己就是改變苗栗的力量。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>一起勇敢，一起寫下歷史，一起贏得苗栗的驕傲！</strong></p>","createdAt":"2022-08-09T05:47:42.689Z"},"candidateEducations":[{"id":1029,"title":"中正大學法研所公法組碩士畢業","content":null,"weight":3,"createdAt":"2022-08-09T05:47:42.820Z"},{"id":1028,"title":"中正大學勞工關係系、法律系雙主修畢業","content":null,"weight":2,"createdAt":"2022-08-09T05:47:42.778Z"},{"id":1027,"title":"新竹中學畢業","content":null,"weight":1,"createdAt":"2022-08-09T05:47:42.725Z"}],"candidateExperiences":[{"id":1085,"title":"現任時代力量苗栗縣議員","content":null,"weight":2,"createdAt":"2022-08-09T05:47:42.794Z"},{"id":1115,"title":"雪谷南榕法律事務所律師","content":null,"weight":1,"createdAt":"2022-08-16T01:24:26.169Z"}],"candidatePolitics":[{"id":1094,"title":"擺脫金權政治","content":" ","weight":3,"createdAt":"2022-08-16T01:34:45.370Z"},{"id":1095,"title":"擺脫派系政治","content":" ","weight":2,"createdAt":"2022-08-16T01:35:05.246Z"},{"id":1096,"title":"擺脫黑箱政治","content":" ","weight":1,"createdAt":"2022-08-16T01:35:25.448Z"}],"candidateSocial":{"id":994,"line":null,"facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/kds.miaoli","email":"skdcouncilor@gmail.com","instagram":"https://www.instagram.com/kd.sung/","youtube":"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyKloeGCRDOQUhJ7jirTN3Q","createdAt":"2022-08-09T05:47:42.740Z"},"candidateSupports":[{"id":1023,"title":"看板和志工應援","content":"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdXde6JTo0nRmflwXN_46E-1GtJFy22kbNZm5t13iTXm6RVFA/viewform?fbclid=IwAR17gEuYsF0zbPLh5aOP9KqoP6hAtFLaw8zfBvVDXEAIYi54tt3X_efBiMQ","weight":2,"createdAt":"2022-08-09T05:47:42.798Z"},{"id":1022,"title":"政治獻金專戶","content":"https://donate.newebpay.com/SONGGUODING/GOGOGO?fbclid=IwAR2tT6o9OE8xq7NfoT1HKR0ek7aFR4kD5ND8-JTk-xOsJwVzGIT7eoLBggA","weight":1,"createdAt":"2022-08-09T05:47:42.738Z"}]}}